OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK's first drug consumption
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Froom to get go-ahead       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The UK's first official consumption    
OL,6, room for illegal drugs including heroin
OL,7, and cocaine is expected to be approved 
OL,8, by authorities in Glasgow later.       
OL,10,FThe facility is backed by the Scottish 
OL,11,Fgovernment as a way to tackle the      
OL,12,Fcountry's drugs deaths crisis.         
OL,14,FIt would involve users taking their own
OL,15,Fdrugs in a hygienic environment under  
OL,16,Fthe supervision of trained health      
OL,17,Fprofessionals.                         
OL,19,FA health centre in the east end of the 
OL,20,Fcity will be used for a pilot scheme.  
